ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.group

Class SRR_S01_RESOURCES

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.group.SRR_S01_RESOURCES
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class SRR_S01_RESOURCES
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a SRR_S01_RESOURCES group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: RGS (Resource Group)
    • 2: SRR_S01_SERVICE (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 3: SRR_S01_GENERAL_RESOURCE (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 4: SRR_S01_LOCATION_RESOURCE (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 5: SRR_S01_PERSONNEL_RESOURCE (a Group object) optional repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
